'From Squeak3.6beta of ''4 July 2003'' [latest update: #5373] on 5 August 2003 at 2:27:03 am'!"Change Set:		StreamBugFixDate:			5 August 2003Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a bug in ReadWriteStream's>>next: N implementation if invoked right after writing something."!!ReadWriteStream methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 8/5/2003 02:23'!next: anInteger 	"Answer the next anInteger elements of my collection.  overriden for efficiency"	| ans endPosition |	readLimit := readLimit max: position.	endPosition _ position + anInteger  min:  readLimit.	ans _ collection copyFrom: position+1 to: endPosition.	position _ endPosition.	^ans! !